timeStamps.text: The movie opens in outer space with the starship Avalon
heading to the colony world of Homestead II during a mass exodus of Earth's population.
The ship is on autopilot mode
and the 5,000 passengers are all in hibernation pods for the 120-year journey.
The ship travels through a meteor storm,
and power is diverted to the forward shields
then the ship collides with a large meteor
and the ship vibrates and the power blinks
